title: DPS-BEST OF- Oct 23, 2020
itunes:title: DPS-BEST OF- Oct 23, 2020
description:
On Today's episode of the Dan Patrick Show, DP recaps last night's Eagles/Giants game and previews opening week in Big Ten Football. Can the Eagles maintain their lead in the NFC East? Will the BIG Ten have enough games to make a run at the National Championship? We're joined by former NFL lineman Ross Tucker, Pro Football Talk's Mike Florio, Former NFL QB Brady Quinn and MLB Commissioner Rob Manfred. Plus, Todd has Mock Headlines based on last night's game and the debate.
